testcase.name: loadDataAndRegister should load the csv file register it as a table 'airtraffic' and finally return a DataFrame
flightCount should calculate the total flighttime per airplane
cancelledDueToSecurity should produce a DataFrame having all of the flights which were cancelled due to security
longestWeatherDelay should calculate the maximux weather delay
didNotFly should calculate which airliners didn't fly
flightsFromVegasToJFK should tell which airliners travel from Vegas to JFK and how often
timeSpentTaxiing should tell by airport how long airplanes taxi by average
